HEADWORD: Definable
<hw>De*fin"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Define</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable of being defined, limited, or
explained; determinable; describable by definition; ascertainable;
<as>as, <ex>definable</ex> limits; <ex>definable</ex> distinctions or
regulations; <ex>definable</ex> words</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>De*fin"a*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

